OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777306270
OL,3,CTeenager killed after car left
OL,4,Cmotorway and caught fire
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old woman has died after
OL,7,Fher car left the M4 in Wiltshire and
OL,8,Fcaught fire.
OL,10,FWiltshire Police said the crash
OL,11,Fhappened on the westbound carriageway
OL,12,Fof the motorway between junction 16
OL,13,Ffor Swindon and junction 17 for
OL,14,FChippenham, at around 5.35pm, on
OL,15,FSunday 26 April.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the force said: "We
OL,18,Fresponded after a Vauxhall Corsa left
OL,19,Fthe carriageway and caught alight.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
