CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777306270
OL,3,CTeenager killed after car left
OL,4,Cmotorway and caught fire
OL,6,F"The driver, an 18-year-old woman,
OL,7,Fsadly died at the scene. Her next of
OL,8,Fkin have been informed and our
OL,9,Fthoughts are with them at this tragic
OL,10,Ftime."
OL,12,FWiltshire Police said recovery of the
OL,13,Fvehicle remains ongoing.
