FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777306270
OL,3,CTeenager killed after car left
OL,4,Cmotorway and caught fire
OL,6,FThe motorway has been closed in both
OL,7,Fdirections to allow specialist
OL,8,Fmachinery to recover the vehicle from
OL,9,Fthe embankment.
OL,11,FThe force said it is currently unknown
OL,12,Fhow long the closure will need to
OL,13,Fremain in place, and has advised
OL,14,Fdrivers to allow extra time for their
OL,15,Fjourneys.
OL,17,FNational Highways said westbound
OL,18,Ftraffic will be diverted at junction
OL,19,F16 and routed via the A3102, B4042 and
OL,20,FA429 to re-join the motorway at
OL,21,Fjunction 17.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
