OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1777306270
OL,3,CTeenager killed after car left
OL,4,Cmotorway and caught fire
OL,6,FVehicles over 4.2m (13ft) in height
OL,7,Fwill be diverted via the A3102, A4 and
OL,8,FA350. The eastbound diversions will
OL,9,Foperate in reverse.
OL,11,FPolice have appealed for any witnesses
OL,12,For anyone with dashcam footage to
OL,13,Fcontact the force.
